  "Use existing utilities instead of creating new ones.",
  "Keep file names consistent with component names.",
  "Do not put business logic in libs/ — library configs only.",
  "Do not put feature components in components/ui/ — shadcn primitives only.",
  "Do not create inline interfaces in service files — use src/interfaces/.",
  "Never skip barrel exports (index.ts) when adding to interfaces/, services/, or utils/.",
];

